data.title: MY BLOCK MY HOOD MY CITY
data.meta_description: Taking Care of People, No Matter What. Support M3 in working with youth and communities all over Chicago.
data.meta_site_name: MY BLOCK MY HOOD MY CITY
data.text:
My Block My Hood My City is here to start the conversations that cultivate a deeper connection to our communities and the people within them in order to ensure everyone has what they need to succeed. We work tirelessly to empower our neighbors with knowledge and inspire them with opportunity so they can take positive action with confidence, creating a new world of possibilities for themselves and their families - and ultimately, the block, the hood, and the city, too.

Our volunteering efforts.

We believe that the city reflects who we are, and we have a responsibility to what it is. Therefore we host multiple volunteer events per month through our Community Development Initiatives. We support Chicago communities by cleaning alleys, mowing lawns, shoveling for seniors, and more.
